
Here is the instructions on how to set up and run django
1. Install python environment, add rest_framework  (Create folder for todo_api use django framework);
2. Create api folder and create database schema(Create new folder named api and run py manage.py migrate and run python manage.py makemigrations);
3. Create model for class (Creating model for class todo)
4. Create urls and serializers file (Creating urls file in api folder and path. Create serializers file in api folder);
5. Edit setting and add class get and update (Edit api in setting and add class to get the data with create and update delete the data);
6. Update django cors
7. py manage.py runserver